<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Course Created Successfully</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .success-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #faf5ff 0%, #f3e8ff 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #8b5cf6;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .success-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .success-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #5b21b6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .success-message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #6b21a8;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .course-details {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .course-details h4 {
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            width: 120px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #4b5563;
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .course-title-highlight {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #5b21b6;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #faf5ff;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
            margin: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #ecfdf5;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
        }
        
        .next-steps h4 {
            color: #047857;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .steps-list {
            list-style: none;
            counter-reset: step-counter;
        }
        
        .steps-list li {
            counter-increment: step-counter;
            padding: 10px 0;
            color: #065f46;
            padding-left: 40px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .steps-list li:before {
            content: counter(step-counter);
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            color: white;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #8b5cf6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .success-card {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .success-title {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .detail-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 5px;
            }
            
            .detail-label {
                width: auto;
            }
            
            .cta-button {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸŽ¯ Course Created!</h1>
            <p>Your learning content is ready to inspire</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello {{creatorFirstName}},
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                ðŸŽ‰ Incredible work! You've just created something amazing that has the power to transform minds and change lives. Your course isn't just content - it's a gateway to knowledge, growth, and success for everyone who experiences it. We're genuinely excited to see the impact you're going to make!
            </div>
            
            <div class="success-card">
                <div class="success-icon">ðŸš€</div>
                <div class="success-title">Course Successfully Created!</div>
                <div class="success-message">
                    Your learning masterpiece is now live and ready to inspire learners. Every lesson you've crafted, every detail you've considered - it all comes together to create an experience that will empower others to achieve their goals.
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="course-title-highlight">
                "{{title}}"
            </div>
            
            <div class="course-details">
                <h4>Course Information</h4>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Title:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{title}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Description:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{description}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Creator:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{creatorFirstName}} {{creatorLastName}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if organizationName}}
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Organization:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{organizationName}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if branchName}}
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Branch:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{branchName}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{courseUrl}}" class="cta-button">View Your Course</a>
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button">Go to Dashboard</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h4>What's Next?</h4>
                <ol class="steps-list">
                    <li>Review your course content and make any final adjustments</li>
                    <li>Add learning materials, resources, and supplementary content</li>
                    <li>Create engaging assessments and quizzes for your learners</li>
                    <li>Invite learners to enroll and begin their learning journey</li>
                    <li>Monitor progress and engagement through your analytics dashboard</li>
                    <li>Gather feedback to continuously improve the learning experience</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <strong>Why your course matters:</strong> In a world hungry for knowledge and growth, you've just created a resource that can unlock potential and open doors. Every person who takes your course will carry forward the knowledge you've shared, creating a ripple effect of learning and achievement that extends far beyond what you can imagine.
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <strong>Your educator's toolkit is powerful:</strong> You now have access to comprehensive analytics to track learner engagement, progress monitoring tools to ensure success, and communication features to build a vibrant learning community. Use these insights to refine your approach and maximize the impact of your teaching.
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                Thank you for choosing to share your expertise and passion with others. Educators like you are the driving force behind personal and professional transformation. We're honored to provide the platform for your vision, and we can't wait to see the success stories that emerge from your course! ðŸŒŸ
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>
                {{companyName}} | 
                {{#if unsubscribeUrl}}<a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a>{{/if}}
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 